{"id": 2077, "genre": 1000, "title": "皮克斯的动画片看了这么多年，你对它都有什么想说的？", "description": "你选择看/不看的点，都是什么？没说到的请在评论区补充！（题图来自：GIPHY)", "record_count": 8270, "comment_count": 35, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171220122732I9h3Mo0JGqnREF8c.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-20T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3451, "title": "皮克斯的动画片看了这么多年，你对它都有什么想说的？", "content": "皮克斯的动画片看了这么多年，你对它都有什么想说的？                                                               ", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 255266, "content": "总是“历尽艰难初心不改”故事套路", "image": "img/option/option/20171220123643EILXUAm1hVHY3kar.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 255276, "content": "逻辑大体通顺，但不能深究，coco不恨爸爸为啥不早挂他照片", "image": "img/option/option/201712201234447CQ25IZzKEbsgc4R.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 255271, "content": "别再盯着汽车系列炒冷饭了", "image": "img/option/option/201712201744291i9z6D7tBqmRc8fx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 255272, "content": "虽然“总动员”是皮克斯标志，但总译成这样有点傻", "image": "img/option/option/20171220123905YKM4vxFRGm1VhJpw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 255387, "content": "还好设定和画面永远在水准，仍然次次有惊喜", "image": "img/option/option/20171220171209C7ZnuVhiPajo4UbB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 255275, "content": "每部都藏着好多彩蛋，老粉找 A113 什么的一本满足", "image": "img/option/option/20171220174353Ok6YsSIy3NBnPLog.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 255278, "content": "原创音乐超棒，期待更多音乐和电影的完美配合", "image": "img/option/option/20171220123519gK4ydPMwmzpcJR7s.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 255302, "content": "和朋友看电影选皮克斯不会错，不同品味都hold住", "image": "img/option/option/20171220174055WH4Yjmf9zxLNc5GF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 255279, "content": "全年龄段通吃，节假日带全家一起看正合适，感恩", "image": "img/option/option/20171220123543zuqmXWSL05T7QeN9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "se